---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Case Studies — B2B Digital Factory Results | Square Root SEO" description="See how Square Root SEO has helped 50+ B2B manufacturers generate qualified leads from Google. Real case studies with real results." activePage="case-studies">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">Proven Results</span>
    <h1>Digital Factory <span class="p1-clr">Case Studies</span></h1>
    <p class="page-hero__sub">Real numbers. Real manufacturers. Real growth. Here's how we've helped B2B businesses generate qualified leads from Google.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-studies-section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Case 1: Corrugated Packaging -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #206dff;">
        <span class="case-card__badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-box"></i> Packaging</span>
        <h3>Corrugated Box Manufacturer, Indore</h3>
        <p>A mid-sized corrugated packaging manufacturer with 15+ years of experience, entirely dependent on trade shows and word-of-mouth for new business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Zero online presence. No website traffic. 100% reliance on offline referrals and third-party marketplace listings costing ₹50K+/month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Full website rebuild with 30+ product pages targeting "corrugated box manufacturer", "custom packaging supplier" keywords. CRM + WhatsApp integration for instant lead capture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>420%</span> Traffic Increase</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>3-4</span> Weekly Leads</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>60%</span> Lower CPL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 2: Industrial Supplies -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #ffb525;">
        <span class="case-card__badge" style="background:var(--p3-clr); color:var(--n900-clr);"><i class="fa-solid fa-gear"></i> Industrial Supplies</span>
        <h3>Industrial Hardware Supplier, Pune</h3>
        <p>A B2B distributor of industrial fasteners, bearings, and tools, competing against large online catalogues with no digital strategy of their own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Website existed but ranked for zero keywords. Losing deals to competitors who appeared on page 1 of Google. No lead tracking system in place.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Keyword mapping for 200+ industrial products. Created category and product pages optimised for procurement-intent searches. Wired GSC + Analytics + CRM.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>300%</span> Traffic Growth</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>Page 1</span> For 40+ Keywords</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>5 Months</span> To ROI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 3: Textiles & Fabrics -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #ec191e;">
        <span class="case-card__badge" style="background:var(--p2-clr);"><i class="fa-solid fa-shirt"></i> Textiles</span>
        <h3>Fabric Manufacturer &amp; Exporter, Surat</h3>
        <p>A fabric manufacturing unit producing polyester, cotton blends, and technical textiles for domestic and international buyers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Website was a static brochure with no SEO. International buyers could not find them. Missed export opportunities due to zero Google visibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Built fabric-type landing pages targeting global buyer queries. E-E-A-T content with certifications and manufacturing capabilities. Multi-language lead forms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>3</span> Export Orders</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>280%</span> Organic Growth</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>4 Months</span> Timeline</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 4: Plastic Packaging -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #206dff;">
        <span class="case-card__badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-recycle"></i> Plastic Packaging</span>
        <h3>BOPP Film &amp; Shrink Wrap Manufacturer, Gujarat</h3>
        <p>A specialty plastic packaging company producing BOPP films, shrink wraps, and custom packaging for FMCG and pharma clients.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Completely dependent on third-party marketplaces and trade fairs. Spending ₹70K+ per month on marketplace leads with low conversion rates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Product-specific landing pages for BOPP film, shrink wrap, stretch film. Technical content showcasing manufacturing capabilities and compliance certifications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>4x</span> Lead Increase</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>70%</span> Marketplace Savings</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>6 Months</span> Full Impact</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 5: Automation -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #ffb525;">
        <span class="case-card__badge" style="background:var(--p3-clr); color:var(--n900-clr);"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i> Automation</span>
        <h3>Industrial Automation Manufacturer, Mumbai</h3>
        <p>A niche manufacturer of PLC panels, SCADA systems, and conveyor automation for factories and warehouses across India.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Highly technical products with very specific buyer intent. Generic SEO agencies failed to understand the niche. No visibility on Google for automation keywords.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Deep technical content for PLC, SCADA, and conveyor systems. Product pages with detailed specifications. Integration with call tracking and WhatsApp for instant enquiries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>500%</span> Traffic Growth</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>Page 1</span> For 25+ Keywords</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>Strongest</span> Pipeline Ever</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case 6: Chemicals -->
    <div class="case-card reveal">
      <div class="case-card__header" style="--case-clr: #ec191e;">
        <span class="case-card__badge" style="background:var(--p2-clr);"><i class="fa-solid fa-flask"></i> Chemicals</span>
        <h3>Specialty Chemicals Manufacturer, Ahmedabad</h3>
        <p>A chemical formulation company supplying specialty chemicals to pharma, FMCG, and industrial clients.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card__body">
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation p2-clr"></i> Challenge</h4>
          <p>Complex product catalogue with hundreds of formulations. No digital strategy. Procurement officers could not discover them on Google.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p1-clr"></i> A.C.I.D Solution</h4>
          <p>Built 40+ product-specific landing pages with chemical specifications, MSDS data, and use-case content. E-E-A-T authority signals with certifications and lab capabilities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__block">
          <h4><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line p3-clr"></i> Results</h4>
          <div class="case-card__stats">
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>40+</span> Landing Pages</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>Pharma</span> Leads Acquired</div>
            <div class="case-card__stat"><span>6 Months</span> To Full ROI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BANNER -->
<section class="page-cta reveal">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Ready to Be Our Next <span class="p3-clr">Success Story?</span></h2>
    <p>We'll build your Digital Factory and get your products on page 1 of Google.</p>
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:30px;">
      <a href="/contact" class="common-btn p3-bg box-style">Build My Digital Factory <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long"></i></a>
      <a href="/acid-test" class="common-btn p1-bg box-style">Take Free ACID Test <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
